{
  "stem": "2226.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- they-- they know me and everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So soon I come in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I say, I talked and talked a little bit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a wheel man comes in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he goes to the oberkapo, to mine oberkapo.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know the-- I know even the number.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had 42-- 40-- no-- 27042.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He's alive.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a very good man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And another one was 27041-- one number different.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when I come over there, that wheel man goes over to that oberman.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, listen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I need some chains-- to make chains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, listen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That he-- he told the-- the to the civil, that oberkapo.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We don't do that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So-- so I told-- I mixed in a little bit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, and he shouldn't do that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I said, listen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I know how to do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I says, if he give me the chain, you got to give me the material on a snow chain.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, it used to be-- not your time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It used to be here snow chain too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You remember the snow chain?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You ever saw a snow chain?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, the cars with lots of snow in Canada.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no snow tires here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was snow chain.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So if that's the case, he said, you can do it?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I says, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I won't think I wouldn't be able to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I need the locks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because if you put them on on the wheels, I make them loose.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then I have to have locks, that the chain should be tight on the wheels-- like that-- turns the wheel and the chain, and they cross-- cross like that-- the chain-- here like that, and here one chain.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the meantime, he brought-- the-- the civil-- the chain.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
